\c 10
\s Ingilosi elogwalo oluncinyane oluvulekileyo
\p
\v 1 Ngasengibona enye ingilosi elamandla isehla ivela ezulwini; yembethe iyezi\x + 1.7.\x*, lomchilowamakhosikazi usekhanda \add layo\x + Hez. 1.28. Isam. 4.3.\x*\add*, lobuso bayo babunjengelanga\x + Mat. 17.2. Isam. 1.16. 12.1.\x*, lenyawo zayo\x + 1.15.\x* zinjengensika zomlilo;
\v 2 njalo yayilogwalo oluncinyane oluvulekileyo esandleni sayo\x + 10.8. Hez. 2.9.\x*; yasimisa unyawo lwayo lokunene phezu kolwandle, lolwekhohlo phezu komhlabathi\x + 10.5,8. Mat. 28.18.\x*,
\v 3 yamemeza ngelizwi elikhulu njengesilwane\x + 5.5.\x* sibhonga\x + Jow. 3.16. Amos 1.2.\x*; kwathi isimemezile, imidumo eyisikhombisa yakhuluma amazwi ayo\x + 6.1.\x*,
\v 4 kwathi imidumo eyisikhombisa isikhulume amazwi ayo, ngasengizabhala; ngasengisizwa ilizwi livela ezulwini\x + 10.8.\x*, lisithi kimi: Namathisela ngophawu izinto imidumo eyisikhombisa ezikhulumileyo\x + Dan. 12.4. Isam. 22.10.\x*, ungazibhali lezizinto.
\p
\v 5 Lengilosi engayibona imi phezu kolwandle laphezu komhlabathi\x + 10.5,8. Mat. 28.18.\x* yaphakamisela isandla sayo ezulwini\x + Dan. 12.7. Gen. 14.22.\x*,
\v 6 yafunga\x + Dan. 12.7. Gen. 14.22.\x* ngaye ophilayo kuze kube nini lanini\x + 4.9.\x*, owadala izulu lezinto ezikulo, lomhlaba lezinto ezikuwo, lolwandle lezinto ezikulo\x + Neh. 9.6. Isam. 4.11.\x*, ukuthi kakusayikuba lesikhathi\x + 12.12. Dan. 12.7. Isam. 16.17; 21.6.\x*;
\v 7 kodwa ensukwini zelizwi lengilosi yesikhombisa\x + 11.15.\x*, isizakhalisa uphondo, kuzabe sekuphelelisiwe imfihlo kaNkulunkulu\x + 17.17.\x*, njengoba watshumayela kwezakhe inceku abaprofethi.
\v 8 Lelizwi engalizwa livela ezulwini\x + 10.8.\x*, lakhuluma lami futhi, lathi: Hamba u\add ye\add*thatha ugwalo oluncinyane oluvulekileyo olusesandleni sengilosi\x + 10.8. Hez. 2.9.\x* emi phezu kolwandle laphezu komhlabathi\x + 10.5,8. Mat. 28.18.\x*.
\v 9 Ngasengisiya engilosini, ngisithi kuyo: Nginika ugwalo oluncinyane. Yasisithi kimi: \add Lu\add*thathe uludle uluqede\x + Hez. 2.8; 3.1. Jer. 15.16.\x*; futhi luzababisa isisu sakho, kodwa emlonyeni wakho luzaba mnandi njengoluju.
\v 10 Ngasengiluthatha ugwalo oluncinyane esandleni sengilosi, ngaludla ngaluqeda\x + Hez. 3.2.\x*, lwaselusiba emlonyeni wami njengoluju, ubunandi\x + Hez. 3.3.\x*; kwathi sengiludlile, isisu sami sababa\x + Hez. 2.10.\x*.
\v 11 Yasisithi kimi: Kumele ukuthi uphinde uprofethe ebantwini lezizweni lezindimini lemakhosini amanengi\x + 5.9.\x*.
